description:
My place is close to Bar 169, The F/J/M/Z/D/B subway lines, Chinatown, LES, East Village, Williamsburg. You’ll love my place because of the coziness and the comfy bed. My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, and business travelers.

name: Cozy Studio in the LES
review: Great location and price. It's Lower East Side living so the place wasn't huge but it was perfect for me and my dog for the week. Rachel was very responsive. Thanks!
